<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>160</hymn_number>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Aa dawh bik Jesuh, Zeizong vialte pengtu, Pathian le minung i Fapa,
 Nangmah kan bochan, Nangmah kan upat, Nang ka thlarau sunpar luchin.

[V2]
 Ram-hring an i dawh, Thing an i dawh chinchin, Sunparnak in an i thuam
 dih, Jesuh aa dawh deuh, Jesuh a thiang deuh, Ngaihchiami lung a lawmhter
 hna.

[V3]
 Nitlang aa dawh ko, Thlapa aa dawh chinchin, Vancung arfi vialte zong
 khi, Vanmi vialte nih, An thangthat leng in, Jesuh cu a thiang i a ceu.</lyrics>
<title>AA DAWH BIK JESUH CH160</title>
</song>